Dim doc As HtmlDocument = hw.Load("http://xxxxxxxxxx/GeneralContent/Active/PrintPage/PrintPage.aspx?PageId=3270")
        ' Get all columns in the document
        Dim table As HtmlNodeCollection = doc.DocumentNode.SelectNodes("//table")
        ' Get the value of the column and print it
        For Each col As HtmlNode In table
 
            Dim rows As HtmlNodeCollection = col.SelectNodes("//tr")
 
            For Each row As HtmlNode In rows
                Dim td As HtmlNodeCollection = row.SelectNodes("//td")
                For Each cell As HtmlNode In td
                    Response.Write(cell.InnerText)
 
                Next
 
            Next
 
        Next
